<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>You running again?<br>
What’s it look like?<br>
Like you’re nothing but a runaway.<br>
Thanks. <br>
Would you stay?<br>
No.<br>
Why not? </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
