We let go as fast as we’d touched.<br>
“Still your girl?” I asked, parroting his words back at him. He looked at the open door behind me.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Allegra</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
