“Give me a reason!”<br>
He stepped toward me and leaned in.<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>All the lights are misty in the river, and all the trees are full of starlight, and all they can gather is the two that matter forever and forever.<br>
A touch.<br>
He dies.<br>
A kiss.<br>
